  "excerpt": "<p>Katie Crafts Valentine’s Picks Valentine’s Day is less than a month away! Oh boy! I’m working on a pretty gift guide that I’ll share with you next week, but today is all about my Valentine’s items! I want you to get a chance to get your orders in so you are set before the big [&hellip;]</p>\n",
  "content": "<p><strong>Katie Crafts Valentine’s Picks<br>\n</strong></p>\n<p>Valentine’s Day is less than a month away! Oh boy! I’m working on a pretty gift guide that I’ll share with you next week, but today is all about my Valentine’s items! I want you to get a chance to get your orders in so you are set before the big day. Check out what <a title=\"Katie Crafts on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/katiecrafts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Katie Crafts Etsy Shop</strong></a> has to offer!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-613800132-oqjm-1.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"525\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-561343014-8tmb-2.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>Score your Valentine a pair of <a title=\"Cupid's Arrow Earrings by Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/192752931/cupids-arrow-dangle-earrings-geometric?ref=shop_home_active_7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cupid’s Arrow Earrings</a>, or perhaps download an <a title=\"All You Need Is Love Instant Download Print\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/178591502/instant-download-all-you-need-is-love?ref=shop_home_feat_4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">“All You Need Is Love”</a> print to frame!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-709271225-ifj0-3.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-709146284-hjh8-4.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>Perhaps a pair of <a title=\"Fabric Covered Button Earrings Vintage Butterflies by Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/186174892/fabric-covered-button-stud-earrings-12?ref=shop_home_active_5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">fabric button earrings</a> with teeny vintage butterflies on them is more your Valentine’s style. Or maybe an <a title=\"Valentine's Day Pantone Color of the Year Hair Bow from Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/212658783/marsala-hair-bow-valentines-day-pantone?ref=shop_home_active_1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">adorable hair bow</a> in this year’s Pantone Color of the Year: Marsala!</p>\n\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-589323817-7g83-5.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-613915287-qcdj-6.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n<p>Send your Valentine a special <a title=\"Octobot Card on Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/100533706/octobot-greeting-card-single-card?ref=shop_home_feat_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">handmade card</a> featuring my little Octobot who is giving you his heart, or order a pair of hammered raw brass <a title=\"Heart and Triangle Earrings on Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/192751751/heart-triangle-earrings-geometric?ref=shop_home_feat_1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">triangle earrings</a> with little hearts on them!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-709262729-kovq-7.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/katie-crafts-valentines-picks/il-570xn-562336706-j12d-8.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Crafts Valentine's Picks; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"570\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>A red and white <a title=\"Red and White polka dotted bow by Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/212651606/red-polka-dotted-hair-bow-valentines-day?ref=shop_home_feat_3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">polka dotted bow</a> would look so cute in your hair on February 14th, just like a <a title=\"Adjustable Pink Rose Ring on Katie Crafts\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/72935819/adjustable-gold-toned-filigree-ring-base?ref=shop_home_active_2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pink rose ring</a> would look great upon your finger!</p>\n<p>Which is your favorite Valentine’s Day item?</p>\n",
